items.title: Relieved Rays return focus to the field
items.summary: On Monday, for the first time in what felt like forever, Tampa Bay's players, coaches and staff could turn their attention back to baseball, hosting the Yankees in the first of three games at the Mets' Citi Field.
items.content: On Monday, for the first time in what felt like forever, Tampa Bay's players, coaches and staff could turn their attention back to baseball, hosting the Yankees in the first of three games at the Mets' Citi Field.

items.title: Meyer to undergo surgery, miss about a year
